### Claude Non-Streaming Request - Anthropic Messages API
### Expected: JSON response with completion

POST {{host}}/v1/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
anthropic-version: 2023-06-01

{
  "model": "claude-sonnet-4-6",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "What is the speed of light?"
    }
  ],
  "stream": false,
  "max_tokens": 100
}

### Claude Streaming Request - Anthropic Messages API
### Expected: SSE stream with Claude event format

POST {{host}}/v1/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
anthropic-version: 2023-06-01

{
  "model": "claude-sonnet-4-6",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Tell me a short joke"
    }
  ],
  "stream": true,
  "max_tokens": 100
}

### Claude with Thinking Mode Enabled
### Expected: Response includes thinking tokens in usage
### Thinking mode adds reasoning tokens to output

POST {{host}}/v1/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
anthropic-version: 2023-06-01

{
  "model": "claude-opus-4-6",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Solve this problem: What is 15 * 23? Show your work."
    }
  ],
  "stream": false,
  "max_tokens": 500,
  "thinking": {
    "type": "enabled",
    "budget_tokens": 400
  }
}

### GPT Rejection - Wrong Protocol
### Expected: 400 error - Non-Claude models only available via /v1/chat/completions
### GPT is routed to chat-completions protocol, not anthropic-messages

POST {{host}}/v1/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
anthropic-version: 2023-06-01

{
  "model": "gpt-4o",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hello GPT"
    }
  ],
  "stream": false,
  "max_tokens": 50
}

### Claude Tool Use - Function Calling
### Expected: Tool result returned in subsequent message

POST {{host}}/v1/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
anthropic-version: 2023-06-01

{
  "model": "claude-sonnet-4-6",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "What is the weather in Tokyo?"
    }
  ],
  "stream": false,
  "max_tokens": 200,
  "tools": [
    {
      "type": "function",
      "name": "get_weather",
      "description": "Get current weather for a city",
      "parameters": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "city": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "The city name"
          },
          "unit": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": ["celsius", "fahrenheit"],
            "description": "Temperature unit"
          }
        },
        "required": ["city"]
      }
    }
  ],
  "tool_choice": {
    "type": "auto"
  }
}
